[ProMED certainly hopes that the children recover completely from the effects of the enterohemorrhagic _E. coli_ infection. It is curious that there is no smoking gun here. That is, if the food at the Spanish resort was the vehicle for the pathogen, why are there no other cases reported? - Mod.LL

